1
00:00:06,620 --> 00:00:07,740
Shen Gu.

2
00:00:08,020 --> 00:00:10,980
What did you wish for?

3
00:00:15,420 --> 00:00:16,860
My wish...

4
00:00:35,300 --> 00:00:38,020
Where are you going to hang it?

5
00:00:41,780 --> 00:00:43,380
Don't take my things.

6
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:45,139
Don't take my jade.

7
00:00:45,140 --> 00:00:47,459
That's Mr. Shen's token for Miss Lin.

8
00:00:47,460 --> 00:00:49,660
It's an heirloom jade
of the Shen family.

9
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:55,420
Grandfather.

10
00:00:55,940 --> 00:00:57,460
Are you alright, Grandfather?

11
00:00:58,020 --> 00:00:59,460
Where did you

12
00:01:00,340 --> 00:01:02,660
get it?

13
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:06,819
A collector in Shen City

14
00:01:06,820 --> 00:01:09,060
invited me to his house.

15
00:01:09,260 --> 00:01:10,660
I spotted this jade at once.

16
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:13,820
It's broken,

17
00:01:14,420 --> 00:01:16,299
but the owner went to great lengths

18
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:17,619
to restore it.

19
00:01:17,620 --> 00:01:19,380
You can tell how much it meant to them.

20
00:01:19,660 --> 00:01:21,140
For some reason,

21
00:01:21,300 --> 00:01:23,220
I just felt a strong connection to it.

22
00:01:26,260 --> 00:01:28,220
This jade is my family heirloom.

23
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:30,819
Today, I give it to you

24
00:01:30,820 --> 00:01:32,180
as a token of my heart.

25
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:44,180
It's really meant for you.

26
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:50,300
Grandfather.

27
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:53,540
If you like it, you can have it.

28
00:01:54,500 --> 00:01:58,620
Keep it. It'll protect you.

29
00:02:03,900 --> 00:02:04,900
Alright.

30
00:02:06,940 --> 00:02:08,580
Mr. Xu, the ladder is here.

31
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:14,980
You have to hang the wish yourself
for it to count.

32
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:17,140
Alright.

33
00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:19,220
Careful.

34
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,220
I'll hold it steady for you.

35
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:24,460
Grandfather.

36
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:34,879
=Echoes of Gang City=

37
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:39,960
=Episode 12=
(Heart Coming Alive)

38
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:44,320
It's been a long time
since I've been back.

39
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:45,620
Slow down.

40
00:03:02,660 --> 00:03:03,700
What's wrong?

41
00:03:05,180 --> 00:03:06,300
Nothing.

42
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:09,300
This building dates back
to the Republican era.

43
00:03:09,380 --> 00:03:11,300
It belonged to someone
who once helped Grandfather.

44
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:13,219
After a fire

45
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,619
took their lives,

46
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:17,780
Grandfather went through a lot
to buy it back

47
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:19,300
and restore it

48
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:21,340
to what it is now.

49
00:03:21,940 --> 00:03:24,300
How is it? Beautiful?

50
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:26,500
I'll show you around.

51
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:35,580
Watch your step, Mr. Xu.

52
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:40,540
You brought him
to the old family home.

53
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:42,900
Looks like you're very satisfied
with Shen Gu.

54
00:03:45,860 --> 00:03:47,900
Every time I see him,

55
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:51,919
I feel like

56
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:54,700
(As Long As You Are Back)
everything was meant to be.

57
00:03:57,380 --> 00:03:58,220
Grandfather.

58
00:03:58,340 --> 00:03:59,380
Grandfather.

59
00:04:01,860 --> 00:04:03,259
Wanxin,

60
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:06,740
settle Shen Gu in here.

61
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:09,979
I'm meeting Qingniao Group's president

62
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:11,859
at 2 PM.

63
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:12,899
That's great.

64
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:14,779
I wanted to thank him in person.

65
00:04:14,780 --> 00:04:17,500
I'll go prepare a gift.

66
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:18,939
No need.

67
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:21,940
I've taken care of it.

68
00:04:22,580 --> 00:04:26,499
You two just got married.
No need to hover around me all day.

69
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:28,700
Go back to your room and rest.

70
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:30,779
Changhe, let's go.

71
00:04:30,780 --> 00:04:31,900
Alright.

72
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,300
Grandfather.

73
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:38,840
(As Long As You Are Back)

74
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:41,740
I'll take you around.

75
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:43,659
I just landed here.

76
00:04:43,660 --> 00:04:45,900
There are things at the office
I need to handle.

77
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,300
How about tonight?

78
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:50,740
It's fine. Work comes first.

79
00:04:51,180 --> 00:04:53,700
Will you be back for dinner?

80
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:55,420
Yes.

81
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:57,700
I'll get going.

82
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,380
Go on.

83
00:05:12,820 --> 00:05:13,940
Boss,

84
00:05:14,020 --> 00:05:15,580
back to the office as fast as possible.

85
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:16,779
Don't keep Grandfather waiting.

86
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:17,900
Yes.

87
00:05:32,220 --> 00:05:33,099
Hello.

88
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:35,500
Welcome to Qingniao Group, Mr. Xu.

89
00:05:35,820 --> 00:05:37,980
Our chairman has been expecting you.

90
00:05:38,580 --> 00:05:39,340
This way, please.

91
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:43,380
Mr. Changhe, please have a seat here.

92
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:18,619
I didn't expect

93
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:21,219
Qingniao's president and I

94
00:06:21,220 --> 00:06:23,780
to walk out of the same house just now.

95
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:26,140
I'm sorry, Grandfather.

96
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:28,660
I haven't had the chance

97
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,820
to tell Wanxin yet.

98
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:37,060
Minghui does have a good prospect,

99
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:41,820
but it shouldn't have been
Qingniao's first choice.

100
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:44,420
If you're the president,

101
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,100
then it all makes sense.

102
00:06:48,020 --> 00:06:50,860
Not entirely because of Wanxin.

103
00:06:51,740 --> 00:06:55,460
Her father had already been in contact
with us before he passed.

104
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:57,899
I've always been the one

105
00:06:57,900 --> 00:06:59,620
handling the cooperation.

106
00:07:00,140 --> 00:07:02,339
Why didn't you tell Wanxin

107
00:07:02,340 --> 00:07:04,740
you're the president?

108
00:07:05,890 --> 00:07:09,500
At first, I just wanted to help her
through the crisis.

109
00:07:10,020 --> 00:07:12,020
I didn't expect her to propose.

110
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:14,260
I couldn't refuse.

111
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,699
After that,

112
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:19,939
I never found the right moment
to tell her.

113
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:22,060
You should tell her soon.

114
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:27,100
Don't let it come between you.

115
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:30,140
I understand, Grandfather.

116
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:33,499
When you left Gang City,

117
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:36,299
you had nothing.

118
00:07:36,300 --> 00:07:38,460
You must've suffered a lot

119
00:07:39,020 --> 00:07:40,820
to get where you are now.

120
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:42,939
Come and sit.

121
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,620
Tell me everything.

122
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:03,739
I, Shen Gu, take thee, Xu Wanxin,

123
00:08:03,740 --> 00:08:06,540
to be my lawful wedded wife.

124
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,699
(Gang City Marriage Registry)

125
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:10,860
- I do.
- I do.

126
00:08:13,450 --> 00:08:17,580
♪A lonely bench on the street corner♪

127
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:21,930
♪Where all feelings come to rest♪

128
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:27,319
♪In the night sky, the moon's trail♪

129
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:31,309
♪Stitches up and soothes my sorrow♪

130
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:34,189
♪The courage to get close to you♪

131
00:08:34,190 --> 00:08:37,820
♪Drives away my hesitation♪

132
00:08:38,540 --> 00:08:40,789
♪Fate turns and brings us together♪

133
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,779
♪I search my memories with all my might♪

134
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:45,689
♪Love catches me off guard♪

135
00:08:45,690 --> 00:08:47,839
♪You, in the album♪

136
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:53,020
♪Shine through my past like starlight♪

137
00:08:53,490 --> 00:08:57,259
♪You fall between light and shadow♪

138
00:08:57,260 --> 00:09:01,259
♪Melting all my fears away♪

139
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:05,029
♪Those youthful, naive memories
are more than enough to heal♪

140
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:09,390
♪I'm lost in them♪

141
00:09:09,450 --> 00:09:13,229
♪The world suddenly has meaning♪

142
00:09:13,230 --> 00:09:18,009
♪Through the pouring rain, I found you♪

143
00:09:18,010 --> 00:09:20,039
♪In the space of our embrace♪

144
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:26,580
♪Stars spill across the sky♪

145
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:34,640
♪Stars spill across the sky♪

146
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:39,550
Grandfather,

147
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:40,980
you've just recovered.

148
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:41,779
Let's head back

149
00:09:41,780 --> 00:09:43,500
and rest.

150
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,820
Alright.

151
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:47,739
Come back to the family house

152
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:50,020
and have dinner together.

153
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:51,180
Okay.

154
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:53,820
Grandfather.

155
00:09:54,340 --> 00:09:55,820
Sorry to interrupt.

156
00:09:56,140 --> 00:09:57,539
Nice to meet you, Grandfather.

157
00:09:57,540 --> 00:10:00,300
Sorry, I need to borrow Shen Gu.

158
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:04,140
We've got a major decision to make.

159
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:08,020
You're the son of the Fang family,
right?

160
00:10:08,060 --> 00:10:08,939
Yes.

161
00:10:08,940 --> 00:10:09,979
You're right.

162
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:10,979
I'm Hongsheng.

163
00:10:10,980 --> 00:10:13,699
I'm Qingniao's CFO and legal director.

164
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:15,020
I'm also his partner.

165
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:16,579
Good.

166
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:18,460
You're following in
your dad's footsteps.

167
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:22,020
But you've got your mom's looks.

168
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:25,140
My mother is pretty.

169
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:27,060
So you're saying you're good-looking?

170
00:10:29,100 --> 00:10:29,579
Very well.

171
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:32,699
It's happy to see by his side.

172
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:34,379
Please don't say that.

173
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:36,820
There are other partners too.

174
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:40,099
But we started the company together.

175
00:10:40,100 --> 00:10:41,420
He can't do without me.

176
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:50,180
Shen Gu is a lucky man.

177
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:52,980
Grandfather. Mr. Changhe.

178
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:54,819
How was it?

179
00:10:54,820 --> 00:10:57,060
How did the meeting go?

180
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:01,499
What do you think

181
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,620
Qingniao's president is like?

182
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:08,100
I've heard he's young,

183
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:09,860
but he makes rare public appearances.

184
00:11:10,220 --> 00:11:12,420
Not much is known about him.

185
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:14,499
But to build a company like this,

186
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:16,500
he must be exceptional.

187
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:21,220
He is young and capable.

188
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:24,219
He chose to keep investing

189
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:26,020
and support us publicly

190
00:11:26,100 --> 00:11:27,740
at our lowest point.

191
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:29,500
He's a man of loyalty.

192
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:33,459
Mr. Xu, Wan Xin.

193
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,379
Today

194
00:11:34,380 --> 00:11:35,419
is a good day.

195
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:36,899
I've had the kitchen prepare

196
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:38,779
your favorite dishes.

197
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:40,779
Make sure you eat well.

198
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:42,220
Thank you, Mr. Changhe.

199
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:43,780
Changhe,

200
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:46,579
since I'm already in Shen City...

201
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,739
Say no more.

202
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,420
I know what you want.

203
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:01,420
You could've come yourself.

204
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:03,179
I wanted to be with her alone.

205
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:05,020
She just wouldn't see me.

206
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:07,900
You're not trying hard enough.

207
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:11,540
There was also a time when you couldn't
get to meet with Xu Wanxin.

208
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,580
She's here.

209
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:31,260
Long time no see, Miss Su.

210
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:34,500
Congratulations, Best Actress Su.

211
00:12:35,940 --> 00:12:37,939
Thank you, Lawyer Fang.

212
00:12:37,940 --> 00:12:39,900
No, no. Please come in.

213
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:41,140
Please, this way.

214
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:48,260
What's wrong?

215
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:53,820
It's so hard to get a meeting with you.

216
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:56,620
Who's the one who needs help here?

217
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:01,900
Of course, he's the one asking you.

218
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,739
I've got photos
of international star Su Mei.

219
00:13:07,740 --> 00:13:09,140
Tomorrow's headline is secured.

220
00:13:13,420 --> 00:13:14,339
Look.

221
00:13:14,340 --> 00:13:15,659
I know you like this.

222
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:17,019
I had it prepared for you.

223
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:18,099
Grandfather,

224
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:21,379
you can eat more,
but go easy on the alcohol.

225
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:24,300
You've just recovered.
You have to be careful.

226
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:28,220
My granddaughter is so sweet.

227
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:33,940
Have Shen Gu's room
at the old family house been arranged?

228
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:36,100
Yes. The guest room is ready.

229
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:38,939
How can a newlywed couple

230
00:13:38,940 --> 00:13:41,420
sleep separately?

231
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:46,540
Right. We're married.

232
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:50,339
I'll accept any condition.

233
00:13:50,340 --> 00:13:52,300
Consider it my wedding gift to you.

234
00:13:53,020 --> 00:13:54,060
Thank you.

235
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:56,420
Where's mine?

236
00:13:57,900 --> 00:13:59,100
Are you married?

237
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:00,539
How about

238
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:02,140
I give you my congratulations?

239
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:03,860
No need.

240
00:14:07,020 --> 00:14:08,099
You guys chat.

241
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:08,900
I'll take off.

242
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:11,060
Something came up?

243
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:15,939
I'm staying at the Xu residence tonight.

244
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:18,020
No one asks.

245
00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:23,300
Has he been like this lately?

246
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:25,699
It's not even that bad today.

247
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,459
Usually, he's showing off everywhere.

248
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:29,340
I'm the biggest victim.

249
00:14:31,380 --> 00:14:32,580
Are you hungry?

250
00:14:33,580 --> 00:14:34,700
Let's eat.

251
00:14:35,420 --> 00:14:36,340
Let's go.

252
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:38,700
Take the seat of honor.

253
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:41,419
Thank you.

254
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:42,540
It's nothing.

255
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:44,980
Here, try this first.

256
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:47,540
Cheese pumpkin.

257
00:14:57,540 --> 00:14:58,979
(Xu Wanxin)
(How can you tell)

258
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,500
(if someone likes you?)

259
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:12,499
(Xi)
(When a guy and a girl)

260
00:15:12,500 --> 00:15:14,500
(start testing each other.)

261
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:15,699
(Why?)

262
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:17,420
(Feeling a spark?)

263
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:19,699
(Let me guess.)

264
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:21,419
(It's someone close to you.)

265
00:15:21,420 --> 00:15:23,860
(His name is Shen Gu.)

266
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:26,900
(Xu Wanxin)
(Nice guess.)

267
00:15:29,838 --> 00:15:35,038
(Xi: Hey, Wanxin.
Are you falling for Shen Gu?)

268
00:15:59,940 --> 00:16:01,060
Hello?

269
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:02,460
Hello?

270
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:04,220
You're back?

271
00:16:04,900 --> 00:16:06,060
I'm downstairs.

272
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:24,420
Want to grab a late-night bite?

273
00:16:26,380 --> 00:16:27,500
Sure.

274
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:12,960
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

275
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:20,040
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

276
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:26,120
♪You turn and look back at me♪

277
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:32,760
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

278
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:39,240
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

279
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:46,000
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

280
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:52,440
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

281
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:59,400
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

282
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:06,760
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

283
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:12,560
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

284
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:19,599
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

285
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:22,479
♪The promise we made♪

286
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:26,159
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

287
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:32,759
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

288
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:39,160
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

289
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:45,879
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

290
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:51,000
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

291
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:54,480
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪

